data.description:
Experience the epitome of luxury living in the Legends with our 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home. This spacious residence offers a top-of-the-line kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a walk-in pantry, making it perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The open floor plan ensures a seamless transition between living spaces, creating a welcoming atmosphere for family and friends.

The master suite is a true retreat, featuring a double vanity, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious master bath. Additional amenities include a bonus room for your personal touch and a three-car garage for all your storage needs. Located conveniently near shopping and restaurants, this home combines elegance with practicality. To top it all off with a cherry on top, the seller is willing to contribute in buy-down points by buying down your first few years of interest.

Home is contingent, but still accepting offers. 

Enjoy your virtual walk-through before experiencing it for yourself! Use this link to take you inside! https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=CNfsXCmwFaz
